{"tid":277079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧偉江：堅尼系數無計算資產　不少人是低收入高資產","createTime":"2017-06-09T10:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T13:46:36.000Z","uid":30647,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f1c5424ad209e70cb8fd03e1ad387a21fb1d39","tid":277079,"uid":30647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"咁你想點計啫, 任你嗡啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府統計處公布，反映社會貧富差距的堅尼系數，去年為 0.539，比2011年上升0.002，但如果按除稅及福利轉移後住戶每月收入計算，堅尼系數則為0.473，比2011年減少0.002。<br />\n<br />\n統計處處長鄧偉江說，隨著人口老化問題越來越嚴重，如只看收入差距，將來堅尼系數自然會擴大，但<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為堅尼系數無計算資產，不少人是低收入、高資產，因此認為理解有關數字時，應同時考慮市民的物質生活。<br />\n<br />\n鄧偉江又認為如果計算房屋、醫療、教育的社會福利，市民實際收入差距有所收窄。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335130-20170609.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335130-20170609.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hvP%2BnfRiAtt%2BDbsVJPhKgh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=06e89679\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335130-20170609.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a4b3d722\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335130-20170609.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f5b1488620c7f1965998533e7d47df9d8c756f9b","tid":277079,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"計埋生活指數呀笨"},{"pid":"6f850f4ffe3783af31a11785a80ccd6866979ef0","tid":277079,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ef1d4a6753e17a8b163b1fc9b6444ea023ac7fa","tid":277079,"uid":66714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"係咪暗示支那蝗? 黎香港攞綜援但喺支那有樓有地個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8267a211d7ce434a8de6f8f4598c7f039f8dbe8","tid":27707